Precious Memories of my Brother
Dr. Alan George Filby
10.05.1947 - 15.07.2017
A loving brother to his sister Lynn, his niece Gail, and his nephews Ben, Peter and lain, and his StepMother Joan.
Alan also had a lot of friends in Scotland and England
driving all over the country to see them when he could.
